Setup Instructions
==================

Server-side setup
----------------------------
1. Install Python 2.7 (http://www.python.org/getit/)
2. Install pip (http://www.pip-installer.org/en/latest/installing.html)
3. Run the following command in the same folder that contains `requirements.txt` (if that file exists)

    pip install requirements.txt
    
4. Run the appropriate application (if need be):

    python email_static.py

Client-side setup
-----------------
1. Install bower (http://bower.io)
2. From the same folder that contains `bower.json`, run the following command to install any necessary JavaScript packages:

    bower install

Running the examples
--------------------
1. Open `index.html`
